%% title: Order Lifecycle State Machine
%% type: state-machine
%% keywords: state machine, order, lifecycle, Created, Shipped, Delivered, Cancelled
%% description: Order states — Created → Payment Pending → Confirmed → Shipped → Delivered (with cancel/return paths)
stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Created
    Created --> PaymentPending: Submit order
    PaymentPending --> Confirmed: Payment received
    PaymentPending --> Cancelled: Payment timeout [after 30 min]
    Confirmed --> Shipped: Ship
    Confirmed --> Cancelled: Admin cancel
    Shipped --> Delivered: Deliver
    Shipped --> Returned: Customer return
    Delivered --> [*]
    Delivered --> Returned: Request return
    Cancelled --> [*]
    Returned --> [*]
